---
---
<div class="signal-log">
  <div class="signal-log-header">
    <span>signal_log.md</span>
    <span class="x-close">&times;</span>
  </div>
  <div class="signal-log-body">
    <div class="log-entry">
      <span class="log-date">[2015]<span class="log-label">SIGNAL_START</span></span><br>
      <span class="log-text">Graduated NUS. Started writing ads.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="log-entry">
      <span class="log-date">[2015–17]<span class="log-label">HAVAS_SG</span></span><br>
      <span class="log-text">Grew client IG <span class="hl">4000%</span>. First awards.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="log-entry">
      <span class="log-date">[2018–21]<span class="log-label">BLKJ_SENIOR</span></span><br>
      <span class="log-text">Senior Writer. Led <span class="hl">8 creatives</span>. Award-winning campaigns.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="log-entry">
      <span class="log-date">[2021–22]<span class="log-label">GOOGLE_APAC</span></span><br>
      <span class="log-text"><span class="hl">133 SMEs</span> across APAC. Content at scale.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="log-entry">
      <span class="log-date">[2022–24]<span class="log-label">FREELANCE</span></span><br>
      <span class="log-text"><span class="hl">20+ clients</span>. Strategy, copy, brand.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="log-entry">
      <span class="log-date">[2024]<span class="log-label">PIVOT</span></span><br>
      <span class="log-text">Barcelona. Master's in <span class="hl">Human Interaction &amp; AI</span>.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="log-entry">
      <span class="log-date">[2025–26]<span class="log-label">BUILD_MODE</span></span><br>
      <span class="log-text">Code. Products. AI. <span class="dim">// current</span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="log-blockquote">
      &gt; Decade of signal-making for others.<br>
      &gt; Now designing the signal itself.
    </div>
    <span class="cursor-blink"></span>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .signal-log {
    background: #0C0C0C;
  }

  .signal-log-header {
    padding: 10px 1.2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    color: #555;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .x-close {
    color: #444;
  }

  .signal-log-body {
    padding: 1.2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--green);
    line-height: 2;
    max-height: 480px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    scrollbar-width: thin;
    scrollbar-color: #1a3320 #0C0C0C;
  }

  .signal-log-body::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 6px;
  }

  .signal-log-body::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: #0C0C0C;
  }

  .signal-log-body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: #1a3320;
  }

  .log-entry {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .log-date {
    color: #1a6638;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .log-label {
    color: #00FF66;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-left: 0.3rem;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
  }

  .log-text {
    color: #4daa6a;
  }

  .log-text .dim {
    color: #2a6642;
  }

  .log-text .hl {
    color: #00FF66;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .log-blockquote {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 0.8rem;
    border-left: 2px solid #1a4a2a;
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: #4daa6a;
  }

  .cursor-blink {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px;
    height: 0.85em;
    background: #00FF66;
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
